## Frontend Layout 

Pages to create based on the requirements of the App.

### Part 1: Welcome page set up
1. WelcomePage
    - app title
    - short description
    - buttons: Log in / Sign up / Continue as Guest

2. LoginPage
    - username
    - password
    - login button

3. RegisterPage
    - all required fields(Username, password, password confirmation, Full name, email, phone, full address, AFM)
    - Error messages if a required field is empty
    - submit button

4. PendingApprovalPage
    “Your registration is waiting for admin approval”


### Part 2: Main functionality 

5. HomePage
    - navigation bar
    - featured/recent events
    - quick search
    - (recommended section placeholder for the bonus Part)

6. EventsPage
    - filter sidebar
    - paginated event cards/table
    - search bar

7. EventDetailsPage
    - title, description, categories
    - venue/address/date/time
    - ticket types
    - (image gallery)
    - map placeholder
    - booking section placeholder

8. MyEventsPage
    - organizer’s created events
    - options: create, edit, cancel, delete, see bookings

9. CreateEditEventPage
    - event form
    - ticket types sub-form
    - media upload placeholder

10. MyReservationsPage
    - list of booked events
    - booking status

11. SettingsPage
    - account info
    - password change
    - preferences

12. AdminUsersPage
    - list of users
    - user details
    - approve/reject signup requests

13. MessagesPage
    - inbox
    - sent
    - unread indicator


